The paper discusses the use of LSTM networks for automatic music composition, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
